title: Chicago XIV (15) -- Greatest Hits Volume 2
description:
This has to be my last torrent for today so that I can get to the gym and get to work on my dissertation again.

The last official Columbia album, the chart place reflects the content, topping out at a whopping #71.  Probably reinforced in Columbia&#039;s mind the decision to dump the band.  But they will be back....

WRITE YOUR GOVERNMENT AND DEMAND THAT CHICAGO BE ENTERED INTO THE HALL OF FAME!

Baby What a Big Surprise

Dialogue (Part II)

No Tell Lover

Alive Again

Old Days

If You Leave Me Now

Questions 67 & 68
